title: Rick Ross - She On My Dick Feat. Gucci Mane
text:
1 MAKE IT STOP Rick Ross unleashes titanic "She On My Dick" feat. Gucci Mane. 
Anytime Rick Ross busts out the digital trombones, you know he means business. Trombones serve as the backbone of his newest banger, "She On My Dick" feat. Gucci Mane , which hit digital retailers at the stroke of midnight Monday morning. In some ways it's vintage Rozay, the sort of self-aggrandizing, maximalist tempest Jafar conjured up in Aladdin after he got hold of the magic lamp. 
Ross's album Rather You Than Me is out this Friday. Check out the full tracklist here . Pre-order it on iTunes .
